text:
[Verse]
Footsteps on the moon
Stars in my eyes
Floating in the blue
No need to disguise

[Verse 2]
Weightless in the air
Galaxies so wide
Comets flash a glare
In this cosmic ride

[Chorus]
Spacewalk dream tonight
Shining oh so bright
Dancing in the light
Let’s soar to new heights

[Verse 3]
Planets spinning round
Echoes through the night
Horizons never found
A celestial delight

[Chorus]
Spacewalk dream tonight
Shining oh so bright
Dancing in the light
Let’s soar to new heights

[Bridge]
Through the Milky Way
Chasing stars we'll play
Far from night and day
In our own ballet
title: Spacewalk Dream
